title: Hey! Hustler - Prologue (Single)
description:
"Bearded music for the bearded and beardless alike" 
(I was told we need a catch phrase) 

This is sombre yet hopeful, melodic indie folk music. I know it's a mouthful, but its a good  description. This is some music we recorded live in studio. I hope you enjoy it. 

Also we are on the social  media...
